Contacting Undergraduate Admissions 

Whether you’re a transfer student or a high school senior interested in one of our bachelor's progams, we’re here to help answer questions about applying to UIC.
Need help with the Common Application? Technical issues should be sent to the Common Application helpdesk.
Problems with the my.uic.edu portal account? Technical issues should be sent to the my.uic.edu helpdesk.
 


 




